overview.en: TET is Token Economy Token, is issued by the TokenEconomy.one Certified Economic Service Platform and the TokenFactory.cn Digital Money Factory. It is based on the Ethereum Blockchain token . used in the reform of individuals, organizations and enterprises.
overview.zh: TET 全称Token Economy Token 是由 TokenEconomy.one 通证经济服务平台和 TokenFactory.cn 数字货币工厂发行的，基于以太坊区块链的加密代币。应用于个人，组织和企业的通证经济改革。
